WEBVTT	#Elemental Media Engine(TM) 2.17.0.0

00:00:00.00 --> 00:00:00.51


00:00:00.51 --> 00:00:02.85
Police in upstate New York have found a young girl

00:00:02.85 --> 00:00:04.77
reported missing in 2019.

00:00:04.77 --> 00:00:07.83
The six-year-old was discovered in a secret room hidden

00:00:07.83 --> 00:00:11.04
under a staircase in the home where her biological parents

00:00:11.04 --> 00:00:11.70
were living.

00:00:11.70 --> 00:00:13.69
Police credit an eagle eyed detective

00:00:13.69 --> 00:00:16.23
who noticed an odd section of the staircase that appeared out

00:00:16.23 --> 00:00:16.83
of place.

00:00:16.83 --> 00:00:19.46
And they spotted a blanket.